### PrivacyConfirmed API Testing
### Base URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7002
@contentType = application/json

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus/health

###

### Submit Contact Form - Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "company": "Tech Solutions Inc",
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "email": "john.doe@techsolutions.com"
}

###

### Submit Contact Form - Another Valid Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "company": "Innovative Designs LLC",
  "mobileNumber": "9123456789",
  "email": "jane.smith@innovativedesigns.com"
}

###

### Submit Contact Form - Invalid Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "company": "Test Company",
  "mobileNumber": "9876543210",
  "email": "invalid-email"
}

###

### Submit Contact Form - Invalid Mobile Number
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "company": "Test Company",
  "mobileNumber": "123",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

###

### Submit Contact Form - Missing Fields
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "",
  "company": ""
}

###

### Get All Contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus

###

### Get Contact by ID - Valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus/1

###

### Get Contact by ID - Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus/999

###

### Get Contact by ID - Invalid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contactus/0

###
